4dos 5.95 pre-release. COMMAND.COM 
replacement for DOS, OS/2, Win95. Enhances 
most DOS commands, over 50 new commands. 
Command editing, history, aliases, directory 
navigation, point-and-shoot file selection, 
much more. COMMAND.COM compatible, works with 
DOS 3.0-7.0, Windows 95, Novell DOS, OS/2 2.1 
Warp, Windows 3.x. Pre-release version for 
evaluation and testing, expires July 31, 
1997. 05-27-97 release A.
